Vancouver Canucks Defeat Boston Bruins 3-2 in OT in NHL Playoffs

-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 
2011-06-05T03:02:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-05/vancouver-canucks-defeat-boston-bruins-3-2-in-ot-in-nhl-playoffs.html
The  Vancouver Canucks  defeated the
Boston Bruins 3-2 in overtime on home ice at Rogers Arena in the
National Hockey League Stanley Cup Final.  The Canucks, looking for their first Stanley Cup title,
have a 2-0 lead over the Bruins in the best-of-seven series.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nancy Kercheval at 
 nkercheval@bloomberg.net  